   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T16">Ã la TrÃ¨s-Belle, Ã  la TrÃ¨s-Bonne, Ã  la TrÃ¨s-ChÃ¨re,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T16">Dont le regard divin t&apos;a soudain refleuriÂ ?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:span text:style-name="T16">Nous mettrons notre orgueil Ã  chanter ses louangesÂ ;</text:span></text:p>
